The '''Coruscant Financial Exchange''' was an agency of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], established by the [[Coruscant Financial Exchange Establishment Act]] in the year [[3985 BBY]].<ref name="Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide">''[[Knights of the Old Republic Campaign Guide]]''</ref> It regulated corporate finances throughout the Republic. In [[3963 BBY]] its director was [[Herron Morvis]].

